Package com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport Description

Contains classes and interfaces for communicating data with Intelligence Analysis Platform services.

The basic constructs within the Intelligence Analysis Platform data model are entities (which represent real-world objects), links (which represent associations between entities), and properties (which represent attributes of entities and links):

Items represent the common features of entities and links, which include the properties that both may have. In the Intelligence Analysis Platform data model, properties are stored in cards, either alone or in related groups.
